  "title": "Airport Baggage Handler",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Safely load and unload passengers’ baggage from aircraft cargo holds, baggage carts, and conveyor belts.</li>\n  <li>Sort baggage based on flight destinations and ensure proper tagging to avoid misplacement.</li>\n  <li>Operate baggage carts and other ground handling equipment to move luggage between terminals, aircraft, and baggage claim areas.</li>\n  <li>Manage special or oversized luggage (e.g. sports equipment, strollers) following airport procedures.</li>\n  <li>Assist in locating and retrieving lost or delayed baggage when needed.</li>\n  <li>Follow all airport safety and security protocols to ensure baggage is handled securely and efficiently.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with ground staff, ramp agents, and airline representatives to ensure smooth baggage operations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirement</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to do rotating shifts</li>\n</ul>",
